bilingual.source: I'm going to study History, Science and Chemistry.
bilingual.target: 我要学习历史、科学和化学。

bilingual.source: I'm going to study Physics, Chemistry and Chinese.
bilingual.target: 我要学习物理、化学和中文。

bilingual.source: He's going to study English and I'm going to study Chemistry.
bilingual.target: 他要学习英语，我要学习化学。

bilingual.source: I had a chemistry test right at the end of the first week.
bilingual.target: 我在第一周结束时就有一场化学考试。

bilingual.source: He's going to study English, she's going to study Chemistry and I'm going to study History.
bilingual.target: 他要学习英语，她要学习化学，我要学习历史。

bilingual.source: It was from my chemistry teacher that I learnt how to watch carefully when doing experiments.
bilingual.target: 我从我的化学老师那里，学到了如何在做实验时注意仔细观察。

bilingual.source: Chemists often use formyl groups in synthetic chemistry.
bilingual.target: 化学家们经常在合成化学中使用甲酰基。

bilingual.source: There are many chemical reagents in the organic chemistry lab.
bilingual.target: 有机化学实验室里有很多化学试剂。

bilingual.source: Learning chemical names is important for chemistry students.
bilingual.target: 学习化学名称对化学学生来说很重要。

list.abstract: 语法标注解释 chemistry英音：['kemistri]美音：['kɛmɪstrɪ]
《Chemistry》是韩国的混声组合Trouble Maker于2013年发行的迷你专辑。该专辑是Trouble Maker继2011年第一只专辑《Trouble Maker》发行后, 时隔两年才发行的第2张迷你专辑。

yingyinNormal.en: So that narrowed it down to the geology lab or the chemistry lab.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以就把答案缩小到地质实验室或者化学实验室。

yingyinNormal.en: Farkle's gone. He gave up the chess club. He gave up the chemistry club.
yingyinNormal.zh: 法尔科已死，他退出了象棋社，退出了化学俱乐部。

yingyinNormal.en: And in chemistry, no less. And wouldn't that be unusual? Because you're a physicist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过是化学奖，这是不是很不寻常呢？因为你是个物理学家。

yingyinNormal.en: Uh, I mean, I don't know. Maybe. Mom, I have chemistry, all right? Can't this wait?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不清楚，应该可以吧，妈妈，我还有化学课，好吗？这事不能等等吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. Yes. I'd be a physicist with a Nobel in chemistry. Everyone laugh at the circus freak.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，我是个获得诺贝尔化学奖的物理学家，大家快来嘲笑这个小丑吧。

yingyinNormal.en: The process is highly volatile. If one isn't protected by a specialized helmet, it can affect the brain's chemistry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他的研究过程很不稳定，如果没有专业头盔的保护，将会影响大脑化学反应。

yingyinNormal.en: What's next? This is the very copy of The Handbook of Chemistry and Physics in which I looked up the reaction rates of mendelevium and...
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有啥？就是这本"物理与化学手册"，我用来查生成钔的反应和...

yingyinNormal.en: So, the food industry turned to a new technology based on genetics rather than chemistry, the genetically modified organism, better known as the GMO.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因此,食品产业发明出了一项新技术它的基础是基因技术而不是化学转基因生物其中比较出名的是基因改造生物。

yingyinNormal.en: Is this part of your super-aging? Yes. Yeah, it seemed daunting at first, but then I realized, it's like the chemistry set I had as a kid.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是你保持大脑青春永驻的方式之一吗？没错，一开始我觉得会很难，但之后发现这跟我小时候家里的化学实验装置一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Really? Look, you guys have been to every play I've ever been in, have I ever had chemistry on stage? No. No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真的？你们看过我演的每出戏，我有擦出过火花吗？没有。对吧。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Because she gets full marks in <highlight>chemistry</highlight> every time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因为她每次化学都得满分。

examination_example.sentence: Why does our <highlight>chemistry</highlight> teacher often praise her?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为什么我们的化学老师经常表扬她？
